Definition: without pity
Example: in a merciless manner; he was mercilessly trounced by his opponent in the House
Synonyms: adj, all, merciless, pitilessly, pitiless, unmercifully, unmerciful, remorselessly, remorseless, without, pity, in, a, manner, he, was, trounced, by, his, opponent, the, House
Category: adv.all
